###Making Non-coding RNA (ncRNA) specific GTF files

##Human and Mouse##
grep -vwE "(protein_coding|IG_pseudogene|processed_pseudogene|unprocessed_pseudogene|transcribed_processed_pseudogene|transcribed_unprocessed_pseudogene|transcribed_unitary_pseudogene|translated_processed_pseudogene|polymorphic_pseudogene|TEC|IG_C_gene|IG_D_gene|IG_J_gene|IG_V_gene|IG_LV_gene|TR_C_gene|TR_D_gene|TR_J_gene|TR_V_gene|IG_C_pseudogene|IG_D_pseudogene|IG_V_pseudogene|TR_J_pseudogene|TR_V_pseudogene|translated_unprocessed_pseudogene|unitary_pseudogene|pseudogene)" path/to/file.gtf > path/to/file_ncRNA.gtf
grep -E "(miRNA)" path/to/file.gtf > path/to/file_miRNA.gtf
